st_slappy - simple terminal with some key modifications
-------------------------------------------------------
st is a simple terminal emulator for X which sucks less.

=======================================================
st_slappy is st modified with the following patches
direct from https://st.suckless.org/patches/

st-alpha-0.8.2.diff - transparency (adjustable)
st-boxdraw_v2-0.8.3.diff (boxdraw.c)
st-font2-20190416-ba72400.diff
st-ligatures-boxdraw-20200430-0.8.3.diff
st-scrollback-20200419-72e3f6c.diff
st-scrollback-mouse-20191024-a2c479c.diff
st-scrollback-mouse-altscreen-20200416-5703aa0.diff
st-selectionbg-alpha-0.8.2.diff
st-selectioncolors-0.8.4.diff
st-vertcenter-20180320-6ac8c8a.diff
st-xresources-20200604-9ba7ecf.diff
=======================================================
Other additions direct in config.h:

colorscheme -- solarized (also reads xresources)
font -- JetBrains Mono NL size 14
font2 -- fontawesome (icons) size 11
alt j/k -- keybind for terminal scroll dn/up

======================================================
INSTALL
1. clone - git clone https://github.com/slappy96/st_slappy.git
2. cd st_slappy
3. make
4. sudo make install

UN-INSTALL
1. sudo make uninstall
